"{\"uid\": \"natlawreview.com-article-france-olympic-consulate-begins-operations\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"21New Articles  New Articles  Find Your Next Job !\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 50, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The French government has launched a new Olympic consulate system to process visa applications for the Olympic and Paralympic games in 2024.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991868459432726, \"rank\": 0.0007158781451892994, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Key Points:  Additional Information:The EUagreedin November to introduce an online visa system throughout the Schengen zone.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials stated that a digital system will be more secure and provide additional convenience to travelers by avoiding the need to bring documents or wait for an in-person appointment.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic consulate system represents France's first venture into processing e-visas and a similar digitalized visa process.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998008787779834, \"rank\": 0.00012379100755553285, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials will process short-stay visa applications for accredited individuals and issue e-visas that will be stored directly on participants' official Olympic passes.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BAL Analysis:Travelers should be aware that appointment and processing delays may occur due to the significant increase in visitors during this time.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BAL will continue following developments in the lead-up to the Olympic games and will provide updates as information becomes available.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More Upcoming Events    Sign Up for any (or all) of our 25+ Newsletters    You are responsible for reading, understanding, and agreeing to the National Law Review's (NLR's) and the National Law Forum LLC'sTerms of UseandPrivacy Policybefore using the National Law Review website.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}, {\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"score\": 0.9999999997769464, \"rank\": 2.2277742676564934e-10, \"text\": \"NLR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\"}, {\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The National Law Review is a free-to-use, no-log-indatabaseof legal and business articles.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The content and links onwww.NatLawReview.comare intended for general information purposes only.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Any legal analysis, legislative updates, or other content and links should not be construed as legal or professional advice or a substitute for such advice.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No attorney-client or confidential relationship is formed by the transmission of information between you and the National Law Review website or any of the law firms, attorneys, or other professionals or organizations who include content on the National Law Review website.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}, {\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you require legal or professional advice, kindly contact an attorney or other suitable professional advisor.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some states have laws and ethical rules regarding solicitation and advertisement practices by attorneys and/or other professionals.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The National Law Review is not a law firm nor iswww.NatLawReview.comintended to be a referral service for attorneys and/or other professionals.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2233, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NLR does not wish, nor does it intend, to solicit the business of anyone or to refer anyone to an attorney or other professional.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"score\": 0.9999999997769464, \"rank\": 2.2277742676564934e-10, \"text\": \"NLR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NLR does not answer legal questions nor will we refer you to an attorney or other professional if you request such information from us.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"score\": 0.9999999997769464, \"rank\": 2.2277742676564934e-10, \"text\": \"NLR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under certain state laws, the following statements may be required on this website and we have included them in order to be in full compliance with these rules.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The choice of a lawyer or other professional is an important decision and should not be based solely upon advertisements.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Attorney Advertising Notice: Prior results do not guarantee a similar outcome.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Statement in compliance with Texas Rules of Professional Conduct.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise noted, attorneys are not certified by the Texas Board of Legal Specialization, nor can NLR attest to the accuracy of any notation of Legal Specialization or other Professional Credentials.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"score\": 0.9999999997769464, \"rank\": 2.2277742676564934e-10, \"text\": \"NLR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Case_citation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The National Law Review - National Law Forum LLC 2070 Green Bay Rd., Suite 178, Highland Park, IL 60035\\u00a0 Telephone \\u00a0(708) 357-3317 or\\u00a0toll-free\\u00a0(877)\\u00a0357-3317.\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3284, \"end\": 3307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The National Law Review\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_National_Law_Review\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you would like to contact us via email pleaseclick here.\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a92025 National Law Forum, LLC\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3542, \"end\": 3545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.99